quoteid.name: quoteid
quoteid.description: Unique identifier for the security quote.

type.name: type
type.description: Type of financial statement being reported.

fiscalyear.name: fiscalyear
fiscalyear.description: Fiscal year for which the balance sheet is reported.

fiscalperiod.name: fiscalperiod
fiscalperiod.description: Fiscal period (quarterly or annually) for which the balance sheet is reported.

enddate.name: enddate
enddate.description: End date of the reporting period.

currencyid.name: currencyid
currencyid.description: Identifier for the currency in which financial values are reported.

publishdate.name: publishdate
publishdate.description: Date when the financial statement was published.

totalassets.name: totalassets
totalassets.description: Total assets owned by the company, including both current and non-current assets.

totalcurrentassets.name: totalcurrentassets
totalcurrentassets.description: Total value of current assets, which are expected to be converted into cash within one year.

cashandshortterminvest.name: cashandshortterminvest
cashandshortterminvest.description: Total cash and short-term investments held by the company.

cashequivalents.name: cashequivalents
cashequivalents.description: Cash equivalents, including highly liquid short-term investments with a maturity of three months or less.

shortterminvestments.name: shortterminvestments
shortterminvestments.description: Short-term investments that are expected to be sold or converted to cash within one year.

totalreceivablesnet.name: totalreceivablesnet
totalreceivablesnet.description: Total receivables (net), including accounts receivable and other outstanding amounts due to the company.

accountsrecetradenet.name: accountsrecetradenet
accountsrecetradenet.description: Net value of accounts receivable from trade transactions.

totalinventory.name: totalinventory
totalinventory.description: Total value of inventory owned by the company.

prepaidexpenses.name: prepaidexpenses
prepaidexpenses.description: Total prepaid expenses, including advance payments for goods or services.

othercurrentassetstotal.name: othercurrentassetstotal
othercurrentassetstotal.description: Total value of other current assets not classified under standard categories.

totalnoncurrentassets.name: totalnoncurrentassets
totalnoncurrentassets.description: Total value of non-current assets, including long-term investments and property, plant, and equipment.

ppetotalnet.name: ppetotalnet
ppetotalnet.description: Total net value of property, plant, and equipment (PP&E) after depreciation.

ppetotalgross.name: ppetotalgross
ppetotalgross.description: Total gross value of property, plant, and equipment before depreciation.

accumulateddepreciationtotal.name: accumulateddepreciationtotal
accumulateddepreciationtotal.description: Total accumulated depreciation for property, plant, and equipment.

otherlongtermassetstotal.name: otherlongtermassetstotal
otherlongtermassetstotal.description: Total value of other long-term assets, including intangible assets and deferred tax assets.

totalliabilities.name: totalliabilities
totalliabilities.description: Total liabilities owed by the company, including both current and non-current liabilities.

totalcurrentliabilities.name: totalcurrentliabilities
totalcurrentliabilities.description: Total current liabilities that are due within one year.

accountspayable.name: accountspayable
accountspayable.description: Total accounts payable, representing short-term obligations to suppliers.

accruedexpenses.name: accruedexpenses
accruedexpenses.description: Total accrued expenses, including wages, taxes, and other outstanding obligations.

notespayableshorttermdebt.name: notespayableshorttermdebt
notespayableshorttermdebt.description: Total value of notes payable and short-term debt.

currentportofltdebtcapitalleases.name: currentportofltdebtcapitalleases
currentportofltdebtcapitalleases.description: Current portion of long-term debt and capital lease obligations due within one year.

totalnoncurrentliabilities.name: totalnoncurrentliabilities
totalnoncurrentliabilities.description: Total value of non-current liabilities, including long-term debt and deferred liabilities.

totallongtermdebt.name: totallongtermdebt
totallongtermdebt.description: Total long-term debt obligations of the company.

longtermdebt.name: longtermdebt
longtermdebt.description: Total outstanding long-term debt, excluding the current portion.

totaldebt.name: totaldebt
totaldebt.description: Total outstanding debt, including both short-term and long-term liabilities.

otherliabilitiestotal.name: otherliabilitiestotal
otherliabilitiestotal.description: Total value of other liabilities not classified under standard categories.

totalequity.name: totalequity
totalequity.description: Total shareholders' equity, representing the net value of the company.

totalstockhodersequity.name: totalstockhodersequity
totalstockhodersequity.description: Total value of stockholders' equity, including retained earnings and additional paid-in capital.

commonstock.name: commonstock
commonstock.description: Total value of common stock issued by the company.

additionalpaidincapital.name: additionalpaidincapital
additionalpaidincapital.description: Additional paid-in capital, representing the excess amount received over the par value of stock.

retainedearnings.name: retainedearnings
retainedearnings.description: Total retained earnings, representing accumulated net income that has been reinvested in the business.

otherequitytotal.name: otherequitytotal
otherequitytotal.description: Total value of other equity components, such as treasury stock or accumulated other comprehensive income.

totalliabilitiesshareholdersequity.name: totalliabilitiesshareholdersequity
totalliabilitiesshareholdersequity.description: Total liabilities and shareholders' equity, which should match the total assets in the balance sheet.

totalcommonsharesoutstanding.name: totalcommonsharesoutstanding
totalcommonsharesoutstanding.description: Total number of common shares outstanding in the market.

ticker.name: ticker
ticker.description: Stock ticker symbol representing the company.
